			<div class="content" id="post-content-1093037">
									

<p>I actually suggested "Capacitor Bank Zero" Because, really, how many capacitor banks containing eldritch living lightning are there?</p>
<p>Nusquam wanted awareness of it to begin a few decades ago, I assumed (taking into account the fact that the Foundation's been following this thing for ages before containment became feasible) that the very first place they would build would a) be a prototype for the future and b) Be used on this thing. Thus, Area Zero. If it, somehow, overpowered the containment bank, a secondary area (Bank One/Alpha/Beta/B) would be constructed.</p>
<p>It does not inflate the importance of the SCP, it makes sense (to me).</p>

